org.sql: SELECT members.* FROM members INNER JOIN projects ON projects.id = members.project_id WHERE members.user_id = "$1" AND projects.status <> "$2" AND projects.status <> 9 AND projects.is_public = True AND projects.id NOT IN (SELECT project_id FROM members WHERE user_id IN (36, 12))
